    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0782c18"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>澧州蘇溪<persName key="A009348">元安</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0782c19"/><persName key="A009348">釋元安</persName>，俗姓淡，<placeName key="PL000000042829">鳳翔遊麟</placeName>人也。丱年於<placeName key="PL000000042867"><anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz5"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz5"/>陽<lb
ed="T" n="0782c20"/>懷恩寺</placeName>從兄<persName key="A010615">祐律師</persName>出家。唯經與論，無不<lb
ed="T" n="0782c21"/>窮核。乃問道<persName key="A010616">翠微</persName>，次<persName key="A003627">臨濟</persName>，各飡法味，<anchor xml:id="beg0782sgsz6"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>不</sic><corr>若</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0782sgsz6"/>飫<lb
ed="T" n="0782c22"/>香積之盂也。斵彫復朴，逍遙自如。聞<persName key="A003669">夾山</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0782c23"/>道盛德至，造<placeName key="PL000000029560">澧陽</placeName>當稽問轇轕，又增明淨。<lb
ed="T" n="0782c24"/>後開<placeName key="PL000000029554">樂普山</placeName>，尋居<placeName key="PL000000029555">蘇溪</placeName>，答詶請益，多偶句華<lb
ed="T" n="0782c25"/>美，為四海傳焉。以<date from-iso="+0899-01-20" key="j20494332049461" to-iso="+0899-02-17">昭宗光化元年戊午十二<lb
ed="T" n="0782c26"/>月</date>遷滅，享壽六十五，法臘四十六矣。臨終<lb
ed="T" n="0782c27"/>告眾，頗多警策辭句云。</p>
